DISCLAIMER AND LEGAL NOTICE

IMPORTANT -- READ BEFORE USING THIS SOFTWARE.


1. EXPERIMENTAL SOFTWARE

This software ("zkpoex") is experimental and intended for educational and
research purposes. It is not production software. The Software
operates primarily as a local simulation environment. It does not broadcast
transactions to, or modify state on, any live blockchain network. It may,
however, connect to user-specified JSON-RPC endpoints in order to fetch public
blockchain data (e.g., block headers and Merkle proofs) required to build
inputs for local simulation and proof generation. It is provided for the
following lawful purposes, including:

  - Academic and educational study of smart contract security
  - Authorized security research and penetration testing
  - Responsible and coordinated vulnerability disclosure
  - Participation in legitimate, sanctioned bug bounty programs


