SPECIFIC PROHIBITION ON UNSOLICITED PROOFS ("RANSOMWARE"): You are expressly
prohibited from using this Software to generate proofs that are sent to any
third party without their prior written consent or public invitation (e.g., a
bug bounty policy). Sending an unsolicited proof accompanied by a demand for
payment is defined as "Extortion" under this Agreement.

You agree that any proof generated by this Software for the purpose of
negotiation must be preceded by a "Commitment to Good Faith," wherein the
recipient is notified of the intent to disclose before the proof is presented.


